294
00:13:23,184 --> 00:13:23,832
Here it is...

295
00:13:23,832 --> 00:13:25,503
Can't you see the problem?

296
00:13:26,224 --> 00:13:27,143
Mr. Xie.

297
00:13:27,424 --> 00:13:28,543
You think you can do it all?

298
00:13:28,623 --> 00:13:29,143
Mr. Xie,

299
00:13:29,224 --> 00:13:30,704
I really can't afford more workers.

300
00:13:30,783 --> 00:13:31,903
He said he could handle it,

301
00:13:31,984 --> 00:13:33,023
so I let him work.

302
00:13:33,184 --> 00:13:33,863
I told you.

303
00:13:35,704 --> 00:13:36,663
I'm not a layman.

304
00:13:36,863 --> 00:13:38,296
