- Mr. Ren, pipe down.

306
00:13:39,704 --> 00:13:40,503
Put up or shut up!

307
00:13:40,503 --> 00:13:41,064
Mr. Xie.

308
00:13:41,064 --> 00:13:41,783
Get out of here.

309
00:13:41,783 --> 00:13:42,616
Who are you with?

310
00:13:42,916 --> 00:13:43,416
Mr. Xie.

311
00:13:43,416 --> 00:13:44,600
- Why should I tell you?
- No matter what,

312
00:13:44,600 --> 00:13:46,623
