316
00:13:51,480 --> 00:13:51,984
Mr. Xie.

317
00:13:51,984 --> 00:13:52,424
Get down!

318
00:13:52,424 --> 00:13:53,543
Enough. Don't be angry.

319
00:13:53,543 --> 00:13:53,944
Come on.

320
00:13:53,944 --> 00:13:54,863
Mr. Xie, calm down.

321
00:13:54,863 --> 00:13:55,743
- Let's be clear.
- Mr. Xie.

322
00:13:55,903 --> 00:13:56,663
Calm down.

323
00:13:56,903 --> 00:13:58,663
