340
00:14:32,584 --> 00:14:33,304
Xuemei.

341
00:14:33,944 --> 00:14:34,543
Get lost!

342
00:14:34,903 --> 00:14:36,304
Gao Xuemei, what's gotten into you?

343
00:14:37,263 --> 00:14:37,944
What's wrong?

344
00:14:38,663 --> 00:14:39,584
What do you think?

345
00:14:40,023 --> 00:14:41,023
What are you doing here?

346
00:14:41,503 --> 00:14:42,623
What is this for?

347
00:14:43,424 --> 00:14:44,023
Can't you

348
00:14:44,023 --> 00:14:44,863
