349
00:14:45,584 --> 00:14:46,383
It's a renovation.

350
00:14:46,464 --> 00:14:47,224
A renovation.

351
00:14:47,503 --> 00:14:48,743
Stop trying to fool me.

352
00:14:48,984 --> 00:14:49,783
Listen, Xuemei.

353
00:14:49,824 --> 00:14:50,663
Get out of here!

354
00:14:50,903 --> 00:14:51,543
