369
00:15:12,984 --> 00:15:13,944
Get out!

370
00:15:14,584 --> 00:15:15,263
Get out!

371
00:15:15,704 --> 00:15:16,704
Are you embarrassed?

372
00:15:16,824 --> 00:15:17,863
