376
00:15:21,263 --> 00:15:22,064
Explain it to me!

377
00:15:22,263 --> 00:15:23,064
What should I say?

378
00:15:23,503 --> 00:15:24,863
What do you want me to explain?

379
00:15:25,064 --> 00:15:26,464
Xuemei, you've misunderstood.

380
00:15:26,663 --> 00:15:27,743
- Don't talk.
- Shut up.

381
00:15:28,503 --> 00:15:29,383
You speak.

382
00:15:29,383 --> 00:15:30,464
I'm telling you to speak.

383
00:15:30,863 --> 00:15:32,143
Fine, will you listen to me?

384
00:15:32,503 --> 00:15:33,064
Go ahead.

385
00:15:36,464 --> 00:15:37,944
