387
00:15:39,184 --> 00:15:40,064
What should I explain?

388
00:15:40,263 --> 00:15:42,023
Too ashamed to explain, huh?

389
00:15:42,143 --> 00:15:43,263
It's not like that.

390
00:15:43,384 --> 00:15:44,088
Your business...

391
00:15:44,088 --> 00:15:45,704
Shut... Do you want to speak?

392
00:15:46,304 --> 00:15:47,263
I'll let you speak.

393
00:15:47,903 --> 00:15:50,584
