396
00:15:55,704 --> 00:15:57,064
My money, Gao Xuemei.

397
00:15:57,143 --> 00:15:57,704
Enough!

398
00:15:57,783 --> 00:15:58,344
Stop it!

399
00:15:58,424 --> 00:15:59,304
I gave her my money.

400
00:15:59,584 --> 00:16:01,143
Did you hear him?

401
00:16:01,184 --> 00:16:02,143
Listen to me.

402
00:16:02,143 --> 00:16:02,903
How could he?

403
00:16:02,944 --> 00:16:03,663
Listen to me!

404
00:16:03,743 --> 00:16:04,704
You have no shame.

405
00:16:04,704 --> 00:16:05,263
Listen to me.

406
00:16:05,263 --> 00:16:06,143
What did I do?

407
00:16:06,224 --> 00:16:06,824
Listen,

408
00:16:06,944 --> 00:16:08,143
I lent her money.

409
00:16:08,304 --> 00:16:09,543
Can you look in the face

410
00:16:09,623 --> 00:16:10,824
