411
00:16:11,863 --> 00:16:12,584
I'm off.

412
00:16:12,984 --> 00:16:13,704
Stop!

413
00:16:13,863 --> 00:16:14,383
You're crazy.

414
00:16:14,383 --> 00:16:15,143
You stay here.

415
00:16:15,143 --> 00:16:16,143
'You're crazy'?

416
00:16:16,344 --> 00:16:18,263
This is Lin Dongfu's girlfriend.

417
00:16:18,783 --> 00:16:19,903
Have you no shame?

418
00:16:20,023 --> 00:16:22,824
Enough, Gao Xuemei!
What do you want to hear?

419
00:16:22,903 --> 00:16:23,384
What?

420
00:16:23,384 --> 00:16:24,704
I'll say what you want to hear.

421
00:16:24,704 --> 00:16:25,984
Give me the facts.

422
00:16:27,224 --> 00:16:28,824
I can make you succeed.

423
00:16:28,863 --> 00:16:29,824
I can make her too.

424
00:16:29,984 --> 00:16:30,783
Are you happy now?

425
00:16:31,304 --> 00:16:32,184
Mr. Xie!

426
00:16:32,424 --> 00:16:32,944
Happy?

427
00:16:34,143 --> 00:16:35,984
I didn't lend money to her!

428
00:16:36,064 --> 00:16:36,743
I gave it to her!

429
00:16:36,984 --> 00:16:38,064
Listen, this place

430
00:16:38,263 --> 00:16:39,824
will be called Chun Yan Dance Hall.

431
00:16:40,023 --> 00:16:40,704
It's settled!

432
00:16:40,903 --> 00:16:41,743
- Mr. Xie!
- What?

433
00:16:41,903 --> 00:16:43,224
Satisfied?

434
00:16:43,503 --> 00:16:44,184
I've invested.

435
00:16:44,304 --> 00:16:45,064
It's my business.

436
00:16:50,328 --> 00:16:51,576
(Yan Dance Hall)

437
00:17:03,503 --> 00:17:07,184
Let's divorce tomorrow.
Whoever backs off will be a coward!

438
00:17:10,424 --> 00:17:11,303
Shameless!

439
00:17:12,664 --> 00:17:13,184
Move!

440
00:17:41,543 --> 00:17:42,263
Sorry about that.

441
00:17:54,743 --> 00:17:55,303
Mr. Zheng,

442
00:17:55,503 --> 00:17:57,704
this is the purchase list for this week.

443
00:17:58,144 --> 00:17:58,743
Take a look.

444
00:17:59,303 --> 00:18:00,944
If it looks okay, could you sign it?

445
00:18:01,503 --> 00:18:02,664
Shouldn't Xie sign this?

446
00:18:03,224 --> 00:18:05,063
Yes, but I couldn't find him.

447
00:18:05,343 --> 00:18:06,464
We need it urgently.

448
00:18:09,384 --> 00:18:10,624
Okay, thank you.

449
00:18:17,823 --> 00:18:18,424
Mr. Zheng.

450
00:18:18,984 --> 00:18:19,704
Stamp it.

451
00:18:21,664 --> 00:18:23,384
Isn't procurement Xie's duty?

452
00:18:24,904 --> 00:18:26,384
Mr. Xie took a few days off.

453
00:18:28,864 --> 00:18:29,823
Because of yesterday?

454
00:18:31,384 --> 00:18:33,543
