455
00:18:34,743 --> 00:18:37,984
Will they actually get divorced?

456
00:18:38,543 --> 00:18:39,063
Impossible.

457
00:18:39,904 --> 00:18:41,904
I know Xie and his wife too well.

458
00:18:42,664 --> 00:18:43,984
They've argued fiercely before.

459
00:18:44,583 --> 00:18:45,743
Xie moved out ages ago.

460
00:18:46,296 --> 00:18:47,096
They didn't divorce.

461
00:18:48,543 --> 00:18:50,184
But this time is different.

462
00:18:50,343 --> 00:18:51,783
You mean the thing with Sun Xiaoyan?

463
00:18:52,424 --> 00:18:53,543
That must be a mistake.

464
00:18:54,904 --> 00:18:55,783
I know Xie

465
00:18:56,503 --> 00:18:57,384
very well.

466
00:18:57,583 --> 00:18:59,144
He is a smooth talker,

467
00:18:59,664 --> 00:19:02,224
but he's proper
when it comes to relationships.

468
00:19:05,263 --> 00:19:07,743
Besides, this fight they're having

469
00:19:08,704 --> 00:19:11,543
