486
00:20:36,664 --> 00:20:37,384
Is that all?

487
00:20:37,543 --> 00:20:38,823
What are you trying to do?

488
00:20:39,543 --> 00:20:40,103
What?

489
00:20:41,904 --> 00:20:42,704
