490
00:20:45,783 --> 00:20:46,743
Want to search me?

491
00:20:47,904 --> 00:20:48,904
What did I take?

492
00:20:49,984 --> 00:20:51,583
Alright, take a look.

493
00:20:52,704 --> 00:20:53,823
