500
00:21:10,543 --> 00:21:11,224
Drop the act!

501
00:21:12,152 --> 00:21:12,543
Come on.

502
00:21:12,984 --> 00:21:13,823
Alright, I admit it.

503
00:21:15,103 --> 00:21:15,624
Xie Chunlai!

504
00:21:17,063 --> 00:21:17,984
Move aside!

505
00:21:18,664 --> 00:21:19,263
No!

506
00:21:19,904 --> 00:21:20,543
Move!

507
00:21:25,303 --> 00:21:26,023
