510
00:21:30,704 --> 00:21:32,063
What a flashy dress!

511
00:21:32,263 --> 00:21:34,023
Going for a new life?

512
00:21:34,743 --> 00:21:35,464
Xie Chunlai.

513
00:21:35,864 --> 00:21:37,063
Your new life is coming.

514
00:21:38,103 --> 00:21:39,063
It never ends, right?

515
00:21:39,464 --> 00:21:40,944
Can't you let it go?

516
00:21:41,424 --> 00:21:42,023
Stop it!

517
00:21:42,464 --> 00:21:43,023
I won't

518
00:21:43,023 --> 00:21:43,904
gift something old,

519
00:21:44,263 --> 00:21:45,224
