520
00:21:45,823 --> 00:21:47,864
Nobody wants your flashy clothes.

521
00:21:48,263 --> 00:21:49,303
Flashy clothes?

522
00:21:49,743 --> 00:21:50,783
How dare you!

523
00:21:51,023 --> 00:21:53,904
I'm just fancier
and grander than that woman.

524
00:21:54,303 --> 00:21:55,543
I-I wanted

525
00:21:55,944 --> 00:21:57,224
