526
00:21:57,424 --> 00:21:58,743
Now, I don't want it, okay?

527
00:21:59,103 --> 00:21:59,944
I don't want it!

528
00:22:00,103 --> 00:22:01,543
Satisfied now?

529
00:22:02,103 --> 00:22:03,063
A memento?

530
00:22:03,384 --> 00:22:05,984
Your love for this home is

531
00:22:06,144 --> 00:22:07,384
