536
00:22:13,343 --> 00:22:13,984
My stuff...

537
00:22:14,103 --> 00:22:16,263
Move! You're in the way! Move!

538
00:22:17,503 --> 00:22:18,343
Move aside!

539
00:22:20,343 --> 00:22:21,103
