540
00:22:21,103 --> 00:22:21,944
What do you want?

541
00:22:22,384 --> 00:22:23,063
What do you want?

542
00:22:23,063 --> 00:22:23,783
You took my stuff.

543
00:22:23,783 --> 00:22:24,343
Come on!

544
00:22:24,343 --> 00:22:25,224
